room_title: Escape room "The Highland Multiverse VR" by Digital Escape Rooms in Orlando
room_address: 3873 Avalon Park E. Blvd. Orlando, FL 32828
room_description: This scenario delves deeper into the virtual reality control system that your party has discovered!  Witness your new adventure begin as a stand-alone virtual reality adventure that 1-4 players can participate in at the same time.  You and your team must travel through mystical realms defeating your opponents, solving deviously challenging puzzles, and ultimately escape the fates that have locked you into the mysterious reality-bending realm.
